%I A397189 #6 Jun 22 2026 00:00:10
%S A397189 1,2,21,714,29557,3889084,644959427
%N A397189 Number of directed Hamiltonian paths in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A397189 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
%e A397189 a(3) = 21: equals A396482(3) (undirected) plus nonsymmetric cases counting 2 each instead of 1.
%Y A397189 Cf. A396337 (including non-Hamiltonian), A396482 (undirected), A397190 (directed Hamiltonian cycles), A096969 (wrapping disallowed, not reduced).
%K A397189 nonn,walk,hard,more,new
%O A397189 1,2
%A A397189 _Charles L. Hohn_, Jun 17 2026
